	<h1 class="title">这位玩家，你将在《使命召唤》里看到好莱坞大牌男星</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/img/missing_face.png" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">Chris Suellentrop</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2014-11-04 09:13:41 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/3260/medium/3260.jpg?1436637565" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


